title: Mari Smith
text: Mandy was super helpful today -- it was as though she could totally tell I am an extremely busy business owner and needed to be extremely efficient with my time today. She was expedient, courteous and understanding as we walked through a couple of pertinent matters in a matter of moments. I felt very well taken care of!
